## Container Instances

### Container Instance

```hcl
resource "oci_container_instance_container_instance" "container" {
  compartment_id = var.compartment_id
  display_name  = "my-container"
  availability_domain = "aaaa:US-ASHBURN-AD-1"

  shape = "CI.Standard.E4.Flex"

  shape_config {
    ocpus         = 1
    memory_in_gbs = 2
  }

  container_configurations {
    container_image_name = "nginx:latest"
    display_name       = "nginx"

    port_configurations {
      port = 80
    }

    environment_variables = {
      "ENV" = "prod"
    }
  }

  subnet_ids = [oci_core_subnet.public_subnet.id]
}
```

### Multiple Containers

```hcl
container_configurations {
  # Container 1
  {
    display_name = "web"
    container_image_name = "nginx"
  },
  # Container 2
  {
    display_name = "app"
    container_image_name = "myapp:latest"
  }
}
```
